deploy-environment
******************


Description
===========

The target OCI resources, such as Compute instances, Container Engine
for Kubernetes(OKE) clusters, or Function, where artifacts are
deployed.


Available Commands
==================

* create-compute-instance-environment

* create-function-environment

* create-oke-cluster-environment

* delete

* get

* list

* update

* update-compute-instance-environment

* update-function-environment

* update-oke-cluster-environment
